{"tid":365653,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]貓貓冇痾尿係兜入面","createTime":"2017-08-19T12:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T15:09:17.000Z","uid":131630,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"357f03f2ecaf8f926b1f3302a3532501b8def50d","tid":365653,"uid":131630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:01:17.000Z","msg":"第一次矇矇小姐痾左成大篤尿係紅色地毯到<br />\n但仲有聽到佢刮痧既聲 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/195253_ec9cbdef82679f7875b25dbfee950a3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F195253_ec9cbdef82679f7875b25dbfee950a3c.jpg&h=a5dc69b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以估佢係咪唔知自己未入晒個兜到就痾左<br />\n第二次就奇怪左啲 聽到有刮痧聲就望過去<br />\n已經見到有篤尿仔係地毯到 但係佢仲係入面痾緊<br />\n而個patpat唔係對住門口<br />\n最後佢自己發現痾左係出面 <br />\n好似怕比人話就匿埋左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/195606_200cab0d4736b9b78609515419e859b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F195606_200cab0d4736b9b78609515419e859b3.jpg&h=918c6279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/195617_baa8413388c1b058180470ca74aa30da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F195617_baa8413388c1b058180470ca74aa30da.jpg&h=87c77e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢係摺耳貓，會唔會係有病先甘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定只係大懵唔小心痾左係出面？"},{"pid":"3adc4704f336fdbdfd5f7dd5582eb2598825b484","tid":365653,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:06:40.000Z","msg":"我朋友隻貓之前都係咁，唔知點解唔會企晒入沙盆，前腳入咗去，後腳就企喺沙盆個邊邊，屙晒落地之後，佢又會去挖沙，完全唔理地下篤尿就走，持續一星期後又變返正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd823fe9e2fe1eaafdfd65085f9454fad8495b55","tid":365653,"uid":56544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:07:59.000Z","msg":"佢好內疚咁<br />\n樓主唔好怪佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5fce0bc0fa045c6e18fabe41478ad7eb0a6229","tid":365653,"uid":131630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢好內疚咁<br />\n樓主唔好怪佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放心我好錫佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到佢唔知驚乜真係好好笑好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2eb22d0d51d21f3374ae967652b92346bf8bd8","tid":365653,"uid":131630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我朋友隻貓之前都係咁，唔知點解唔會企晒入沙盆，前腳入咗去，後腳就企喺沙盆個邊邊，屙晒落地之後，佢又會去挖沙，完全唔理地下篤尿就走，持續一星期後又變返正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好彩姐 幾驚係有咩病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1396cb4f52395fcfeb400abf666e2b77d5fe17de","tid":365653,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"可能病變生骨刺痛到行唔到入去屙<br />\n你有無每年照x ray檢查？"},{"pid":"ed0d30b18581b89db7651c25bcdbe50bf0003057","tid":365653,"uid":131630,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能病變生骨刺痛到行唔到入去屙<br />\n你有無每年照x ray檢查？</blockquote><br />\nPlan左遲啲帶佢檢查 <br />\n聽講摺耳多數老左先有骨既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢依加2歲幾 希望係佢太懵先甘樣啦<br />\n打算觀察佢多陣先"},{"pid":"386f3c0d7f1bdfe28942618ab678e17f83b6c325","tid":365653,"uid":21654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可能病變生骨刺痛到行唔到入去屙<br />\n你有無每年照x ray檢查？</blockquote><br />\nPlan左遲啲帶佢檢查 <br />\n聽講摺耳多數老左先有骨既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢依加2歲幾 希望係佢太懵先甘樣啦<br />\n打算觀察佢多陣先</blockquote><br />\n唔係㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係每隻病變時間都唔同<br />\n有啲嚴重嘅出世已經有，由幾個月發病到終生不發病又有<br />\n，唔好等到佢痛到忍唔到先處理，好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左關節，心肌肥大，多囊性腎病都係遺傳，亦唔知幾時發，所以先會有每年檢查呢個需要"},{"pid":"d55ce9b52aa629fa6b7f9f5c3a62285d91330e39","tid":365653,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:50:39.000Z","msg":"我個隻都係摺耳<br />\n少少事都好鬼驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0f2c25ba2ae64277356c8b45dd05b7cf211c27","tid":365653,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:30:48.000Z","msg":"唔好鬧佢啦，好得意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cecb621339f7ba55f121b7c65b104e0d9ffb4b5","tid":365653,"uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw, 摺耳好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記住幫佢絕育"},{"pid":"50197dce8908e3201d5f7b2b11df95e50eea2a38","tid":365653,"uid":4210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:09:17.000Z","msg":"甘你老母"}]}